snippet.title: Nine Parchments: The Astral Challenges Release Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Nine Parchments is a co-operative blast 'em up game of magical mayhem from Frozenbyte. The Astral Challenges is a free content update out now on Nintendo Switch for all Nine Parchments players! New content highlights include:

- Six new Arena levels that will challenge even the most battle-hardened wizard veterans!

- A new unlockable character, Selius, waiting to be discovered in the new arena levels, and along with him you’ll discover new hats, staves and spells.

- The new Quick Chat feature will make talking to your classmates as easy as pressing a button, so get ready to yell at your friends.

Read more about the update at http://www.nineparchments.com
